buy a full working onion shop

Bitcoin support

Receive coins on your terms, I provide multiple ways for redirecting coin to your privately held wallets, whilst providing the on-site wallet private keys or other manual but trust-less methods.

Technical support and incident response, fixes to any bugs will be deployed within 24 hours of reporting
Flexible feature additions. simple enough and can be reused in the system for other vendors,

we will provide you anything within 24h after payment is complete

1 year hosting incl. (after this period it will cost you 300 usd/ year)

please submit us a working email address on the checkout where we can contact you
